title: 7: I'm Drunk, Emotional, and Sharing Way to Much... I’ve been BETRAYED.
description:
Wow, does Sadie have some juicy tea for y'all today. Oh and she’s hammered! Welcome to Sadies first DRUNK episode! Why you may ask? Lets just say she’s got f*cked over big time, and her hearts hurting just a little … (lot).  Listen in to hear the full story, and some very good advice she gives from experiences, enjoy :)
